                              ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/99168840917045402115"
                              key="person_99168840917045402115">Stacey Wise (1783–1842)</persName>
                           in partnership with <persName role="ppm"
                              ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/81168840838645402128"
                              key="person_81168840838645402128">Christopher Patch (fl. 19th
                              c.)</persName> who then operated the Padsole Mill in <placeName
                              ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7011704" key="place_7011704"
                              >Maidstone, Kent</placeName>.</support>
                        <extent>
